channel.title: Z-file searcher
channel.description: Hellooo guys. I have a problem with Z-file searcher. I was an idiot and changed what program it opens with and now it won't work properly. I even reinstalled java thinking that would fix the extension but it didn't. So I'm asking for help, and explaining what I need it a little technical. Basically I just need to know what it opens with, and it's not the java SE platform. Sorry if this is confusing, I was even confused when I chose the jar to run on the java platform, so yeah; hopefully you understand. Thanks ;)
